text: Jesús María, also known as El Zapote, is a town in the municipality of San Martín de Hidalgo in the state of Jalisco, Mexico. It has a population of 278 inhabitants.Jesús María (El Zapote), San Martín Hidalgo, Jalisco ==References== ==External links== *Jesús María (El Zapote) at PueblosAmerica.com Category:Populated places in Jalisco
